      For seller-fulfilled items from Sports collectibles and Entertainment collectibles categories, the sellers need to be informed of the damage / defect within 10 days of delivery.

      Note: - Once the package is received at Amazon Export Sales LLC fulfillment center in the US, it takes 2 (two) business days for the refund to be processed and 2- 4 business days for the refund amount to reflect in your account. - If your return is due to an Amazon error you'll receive a full refund, else the shipping charges (onward & return) along with import fees will be deducted from your refund amount.

      Product description

      Voltas smart AC is the India's first and only voice control enabled AC which works with Alexa enabled devises and also comes with Wi-Fi connectivity. Voltas smart Alexa AC now allows you to operate your AC by giving simple voice commands to Alexa enabled devise and Wi-Fi connectivity gives you the comfort of operating AC remotely. Be the proud owner of Voltas state of the art smart Alexa enabled AC and enjoy superior cooling and comfort.

      From the manufacturer

      Key Features




      Voice Command through Echo

      Switch the alexa enabled Voltas smart AC on or off and change the temperature using voice command through your echo device.

      Operate from Anywhere

      Operate your AC from anywhere, be it while sitting in another room or before coming home.

      Smart Timer

      Save money by running your AC on schedule. Set timing of switching the AC on or off through the timer setting on Voltas smart AC app.

      Read more



      Cool your Room Before you Reach Home

      Instant comfort on scorching heat days is guaranteed since you can cool your room before you reach with the Voltas smart AC app.

      Alexa will Never Leave your AC Running

      If you forget to switch off your AC before leaving home, no worries, the Voltas smart AC app will do it for you.

      Fan Speed Control

      Set fan speed as per your requirement. Operate your Voltas AC at the desired speed using the Voltas smart AC app.

      Read more



      High Ambient Cooling

      Give you instant cooling at even 50C.

      Active Dehumidifier

      Senses the indoor humidity and controls it in monsoon.

      100% Copper

      Copper condenser coil is more durable & delivers efficient cooling.

      Read more



      Sleep Mode

      Maintains a comfortable temperature by cutting excessive cooling and power consumption, so you sleep comfortably all night.

      Dual Display

      Its dual display feature lets you view the set temperature as well as the room temperature simultaneously.

      Self Diagnosis

      Abnormalities and failures are checked by the AC and reset automatically.

      Read more

      Multi Stage Filtration Advantage

      Removes allergens, odours and other harmful particles to give you cool and fresh air.

      Read more
